The Modern GN Loop Prevention Patch

Key Enhancements for this GN Version:
* Preserves GN Internal Tracking: It wraps the existing lambda tracker
(add_gen_dep) to continue alerting GN's background build-scheduler whenever a
brand new system subdirectory is uncovered.
* Preserves Modern C++ Standard Structure: It properly returns data directly
into the inner files.list_value() vector type without mutating the variable
parameters expected by downstream functions.
* Blocks base::FileEnumerator Hidden Traversal: The native traverser function
setup has its recursive boolean argument dropped completely to false across the
board. The custom loop function handles the manual step-through while strictly
avoiding traversing your symlinked paths.

